title: Asnews 2 Pack Laundry Bags, Travel Laundry Bag Dirty Clothes Organizer, Swimming Yoga Bathing Suit Workout Washable Wet Bag, Navy Blue
features: Tough Material: Crafted from high-quality Nylon with a waterproof and thick construction, durable and tear-resistant, the stitching is strong, and the zippers glide smoothly.

Available In Two Convenient Sizes: The large one measuring 23.6*17.7 inches and the small one at 21.7*13.8 inches, compact folded size takes up minimal space in a suitcase, making them ideal for various scenarios like travel, camping, fitness, swim days.

Aesthetic and Functional: Aesthetic effect came from the new technology materials, vibrant colors and forthright detailing like hidden zipper so does not snag on fabrics, sturdy handles making them easy to carry.
Efficient & Compact Laundry Solution: A practical choice for different scenarios. No more mixing dirty close with cleans one and tossing everything straight into the washer.

A Compact and Reliable Companion For Travel: Roomy, durable and the best way to keep your dirty clothes separately from your travel essentials. Compact size for on-the-go storage, easily fitting into your suitcase without taking up valuable space.
